{"id": "art-177", "label": "Art. 177", "title": "Art. 177", "slug": "art-177", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 177 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)<b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>În afar&#259; de <span class=SpellE>eviden&#355;ele</span>\nprev&#259;zute de <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>lege</i>, <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> pe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>\ntrebuie s&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#355;in&#259;</span>:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_83235476\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1990\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_83235476\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)un registru al <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>\ncare s&#259; arate, dup&#259; caz, numele <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nprenumele, codul numeric personal, denumirea, domiciliul sau sediul <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>, precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nv&#259;rs&#259;mintele f&#259;cute în contul <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>.\n<span class=SpellE>Eviden&#355;a</span> <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>\n<span class=SpellE>tranzac&#355;ionate</span> pe o/un <span class=SpellE>pia&#355;&#259;</span>\nreglementat&#259;/sistem alternativ de <span class=SpellE>tranzac&#355;ionare</span>\nse realizeaz&#259; cu respectarea <span class=SpellE>legisla&#355;iei</span>\nspecifice <span class=SpellE>pie&#355;ei</span> de capital;</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>b)un\nregistru al <span class=SpellE>&#351;edin&#355;elor</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ndeliber&#259;rilor adun&#259;rilor generale;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_394331719\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1989\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_394331719\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)un registru al <span class=SpellE>&#351;edin&#355;ei</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> deliber&#259;rilor consiliului de <span\nclass=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>, respectiv ale directoratului <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> consiliului de supraveghere;</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>d)[textul\ndin Art. 177, alin. (1), litera D. din titlul III, capitolul IV, <span\nclass=SpellE>sectiunea</span> VI a fost abrogat la 01-dec-2006 de </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>Art. I, punctul 127. din <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>Legea</i> 441/2006</span><span style='color:black'>]</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_993794684\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1988\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_993794684\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)un registru al deliber&#259;rilor <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nconstat&#259;rilor f&#259;cute de cenzori <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>,\ndup&#259; caz, de auditori interni, în exercitarea mandatului lor;</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1099644916\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1987\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1099644916\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)un registru al <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iunilor</span>,\ncare s&#259; arate totalul <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iunilor</span> emise <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> al celor rambursate, precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nnumele <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> prenumele, denumirea, domiciliul sau\nsediul titularilor, când ele sunt nominative. <span class=SpellE>Eviden&#355;a</span>\n<span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iunilor</span> emise în form&#259;\ndematerializat&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>tranzac&#355;ionate</span>\npe o <span class=SpellE>pia&#355;&#259;</span> reglementat&#259; sau printr-un\nsistem alternativ de <span class=SpellE>tranzac&#355;ionare</span> va fi <span\nclass=SpellE>&#355;inut&#259;</span> conform <span class=SpellE>legisla&#355;iei</span>\nspecifice <span class=SpellE>pie&#355;ei</span> de capital;</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1626328677\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1986\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1626328677\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>g)orice alte registre prev&#259;zute de acte normative\nspeciale.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1099720083\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1985\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1099720083\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Registrele prev&#259;zute la alin. (1) lit. a), b) <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> f) vor fi <span class=SpellE>&#355;inute</span>\nprin grija consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>,\nrespectiv a directoratului, cel prev&#259;zut la lit. c) prin grija organului\nîn cauz&#259;, iar cel prev&#259;zut la lit. e) prin grija cenzorilor sau,\ndup&#259; caz, a auditorilor interni; registrele prev&#259;zute la alin. (1)\nlit. g) vor fi <span class=SpellE>&#355;inute</span> în <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span>\nprev&#259;zute de actele normative respective.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}